behavior transfer_chicken_pasta_to_plate(chicken_pasta:item, plate:item):
    body:
        achieve on(chicken_pasta, plate)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind plate: item where:
            is_plate(plate) and in_dining_room(plate)
        # Select a plate in the dining room

        bind chicken_pasta: item where:
            is_food_chicken(chicken_pasta) 
        
        bind stove: item where:
            is_stove(stove)

        assert is_cooked(chicken_pasta, stove)
        # Select the cooked chicken pasta
        
        transfer_chicken_pasta_to_plate(chicken_pasta, plate)
